  <brief_title>Effects of Pursed-lip Breathing on Exercise Tolerance and Dynamic Hyperinflation in COPD</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Pursed-lip Breathing on Exercise Tolerance and Dynamic Hyperinflation in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</official_title>
